Key to species of southern hemisphere 
<taxonomicName box="[636,771,619,645]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Macrouridae" genus="Macrourus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gadiformes" pageId="10" pageNumber="115" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
